<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,1163,1653]" pageId="7" pageNumber="434">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,275,1472,1498]" pageId="7" pageNumber="434">Notes.</emphasis>
In the absence of material, the discovery of 
<taxonomicName authority="Haenni, 2009" authorityName="Haenni" authorityYear="2009" box="[792,998,1473,1498]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Dilophus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="434" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sardous" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[792,998,1473,1498]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="434">Dilophus sardous</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1005,1098,1472,1498]" pageId="7" pageNumber="434">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1005,1098,1472,1498]" pageId="7" pageNumber="434" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
brings some doubt about the occurrence of the closely related 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Meigen" authorityYear="1804" box="[552,709,1511,1536]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Dilophus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="434" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="femoratus">
<emphasis box="[552,709,1511,1536]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="434">D. femoratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingRegion box="[749,849,1511,1537]" country="Italy" name="Sardegna" pageId="7" pageNumber="434">Sardinia</collectingRegion>
(which however remains possible). The specific identity of the species of this group may only be confirmed by the study of male genitalic characters or by detailed molecular studies. Accordingly, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Meigen" authorityYear="1804" box="[629,782,1589,1614]" class="Insecta" family="Bibionidae" genus="Dilophus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="434" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="femoratus">
<emphasis box="[629,782,1589,1614]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="434">D. femoratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is provisorily deleted from the list of Sardinian species, pending the examination of possible relevant material.
</paragraph>
